author: StarKiller22515
title: water
review: This is great for people wh have LEGO boats or a LEGO city because they can then use it as an ocean. I wouldnt recommnd getting this if you dont have boats or anything like that. I recommend thsi for the LEGO city people who own boats or want to have a swim party.

author: Lego_fan_
title: Blue
review:
Lego set #10714 is a great set for any builder!

This set includes one 32x32 blue baseplate. This set is great for any builder to build any thing they want on it. particularly water stuff. 

Overall i think this set is bunch of fun but seems a little bit expensive.
